NK037(ji)012:1: // dpal ldan phrin las kyi mgon po trak+shada bka' gter
NK037(ji)012:2: lugs srol bzhi'i sgrub thabs rjes gnang dang bcas pa
NK037(ji)012:3: gnam lcags spu gri zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK037(ji)012:5: sangs rgyas kun la phyag 'tshal nas //
NK037(ji)012:6: bstan srung mchog zhig bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)012:7: sgrub thabs mdor bsdus tsam 'bri na //
NK037(ji)012:8: nag po nyid kyis dge legs stsol //
NK037(ji)012:9: trak+shada dwags po lugs spu gri chig shur bka' gter gnyis ldan bshad pa la gsum /
NK037(ji)012:12: rjes su gnang ba'i tshul lo //
NK037(ji)012:14: man+dala dug khrag gis byugs pa la chos 'byung gru
NK037(ji)012:15: gsum mthing nag me ris mtshan pa bris pa'i steng
NK037(ji)012:16: du thod pa'am zangs lcags kyi snod du dmar gtor
NK037(ji)012:17: zur gsum rno dbal can me ri sha khrag dar
NK037(ji)012:19: mdun du sman raka gtor gsum /
NK037(ji)012:20: drag po'i nyer spyod rnams bsham mo //
NK037(ji)012:22: bdag bskyed bka' brgyad phyag rgya rkyang sgrub kyis mtshon
NK037(ji)012:23: pa'i he ru ka'i rigs gang yang rung ba'i sgom
NK037(ji)012:26: badz+ra a mri ta sogs kyis bsang /
NK037(ji)012:28: stong pa'i ngang las h'u las gnas khang dur khrod
NK037(ji)012:29: drag po'i rgyan bkod tshad med pa dang ldan pa'i
NK037(ji)012:30: dbus su / h'u yig nag po dpag tu med
NK037(ji)012:31: pa las byung ba'i phyi nang mchod pa'i dam rdzas
NK037(ji)012:32: mkha' dbyings kun tu rgyas par gang bar gyur /
NK037(ji)012:34: shap+da pany+tsa k+aa ma gu na +aahmh'u /
NK037(ji)012:38: yam ram kam las rlung me thod pa'i sgyed pu
NK037(ji)012:39: gsum gyi steng du a las k+aa pa la'i nang
NK037(ji)012:40: du sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga rnams bskol zhing 'od
NK037(ji)012:41: du zhu ba las byung ba'i ye shes kyi bdud
NK037(ji)012:42: rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK037(ji)012:43: ma h+aa ba lim ta te jo ba lim ta
NK037(ji)012:44: ba la ba te gu h+ye sid+d+hi sa ma ya
NK037(ji)012:45: h'u h+r+aihth+aa / +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK037(ji)012:46: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK037(ji)012:47: sngags rnams lan gsum re brjod pas byin brlab bo //
NK037(ji)012:49: swa b+h+aa was stong par sbyang /
NK037(ji)012:50: stong pa'i ngang las thod mkhar 'bar ba'i nang du nag po gru gsum gyi gzhal yas khang /
NK037(ji)012:51: de'i nang du mi ro rta ro brtsigs pa'i gdan la pad nyi'i steng du /
NK037(ji)012:52: ram las dpal mgon po sku mdog dus mtha'i sprin ltar gnag pa /
NK037(ji)012:53: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas rtse gsum gyi mgul du
NK037(ji)012:54: mi mgo dpyangs pa ru dar nag po dang bcas
NK037(ji)012:55: pa phyar zhing / g.yon dgra bgegs kyi glo snying
NK037(ji)012:56: rlangs pa bun ne zhal du gsol zhing bdud zhags
NK037(ji)012:58: sku la dar nag gi 'jol ber gsum brtsegs su gsol zhing /
NK037(ji)012:59: rin po che gser gyi ska rags bcings pa /
NK037(ji)012:60: zhabs la lhwam yu ring gsol zhing /
NK037(ji)012:61: lcags kyi ral pa mun ltar gtibs pa /
NK037(ji)012:62: mche gtsigs spyan gsum sma ra 'bar zhing /
NK037(ji)012:63: thod skam gyi dbu rgyan dang thod rlon gyi do shal can /
NK037(ji)012:64: rta nag chibs shing rdzu 'phrul dang drag shul che ba /
NK037(ji)012:65: me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs shing bka' nyan
NK037(ji)012:66: las byed sprul pa yang sprul gyi 'khor dang bcas
NK037(ji)012:67: pa'o // rang gi snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK037(ji)012:68: dur khrod chen po u tsa la nas /
NK037(ji)012:69: nag po chen po 'khor bcas spyan drangs par bsam /
NK037(ji)012:71: u tsa la yi dur khrod nas sogs sam /
NK037(ji)012:74: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK037(ji)012:75: dpal ldan mgon po spyan 'dren na //
NK037(ji)012:76: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)012:77: mchod pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)012:78: ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada sa pa ri w+aa ra
NK037(ji)012:79: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh gnyis su med
NK037(ji)012:80: par thim / rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yi //
NK037(ji)012:81: lha rdzas bzang po'i nyer spyod 'di //
NK037(ji)012:83: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK037(ji)012:84: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada sa pa ri b+aa ra a r+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK037(ji)012:86: des nang mchod ces bsgyur ba dang /
NK037(ji)012:88: pany+tsa k+aa ma gu na ma h+aa a mri ta p+au dzahhoh zhes pas mchod /
NK037(ji)012:91: ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:94: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:98: ram las byung ba'i stobs po che //
NK037(ji)012:99: bdud kyi rgyal po khro gtum can //
NK037(ji)012:100: rta nag zhon pa rdzu 'phrul che //
NK037(ji)012:101: sdig can sgrol mdzad khyod la bstod //
NK037(ji)012:102: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)012:104: gtor chog tsam yin na rjes chog bya ba las bzlas pa sogs mi dgos /
NK037(ji)012:106: bdag bskyed kyi thugs ka'i 'od zer phog pas sngon
NK037(ji)012:107: gyi dam bca' dran te thugs rgyud bskul bar mos
NK037(ji)012:108: la / ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada ma h+aa k+aa
NK037(ji)012:109: la sid+d+hi tri yam du dzahdzah zhes snying po cung
NK037(ji)012:110: la / zad bazla'o // slob ma'i don du bgegs
NK037(ji)012:111: gtor sngon du btang ba'i phyag len mdzad kyang don
NK037(ji)012:112: la khyad par med pas spyi ltar yang rung ngo
NK037(ji)012:113: la / zad bazla'o // // gsum pa ni /
NK037(ji)012:115: sngar ma song na bgegs gtor btang la drag sngags kyis bskrad /
NK037(ji)012:118: de'ang dpal chen he ru ka nyid bdag 'dzin ru
NK037(ji)012:119: dra gdug pa can rnams 'dul ba'i don du gnyis
NK037(ji)012:120: med ye shes kyi mgon po 'chol ba'i khro rgyal
NK037(ji)012:121: chen po'i skur sprul pa ni dpal mgon ma ning
NK037(ji)012:123: de las kyang phrin las rnam bzhi myur mgyogs su
NK037(ji)012:124: sgrub pa'i ched du sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK037(ji)012:125: las kyi mgon po sde lnga yang sprul du byung
NK037(ji)012:126: ba las / dpal ldan phrin las kyi mgon po
NK037(ji)012:127: mig gsum dbang po trak+shada nag po 'di ni ye
NK037(ji)012:128: shes mgon po phal mo che'i phrin las pa'i rnam
NK037(ji)012:129: 'gyur du'ang bstan pas mngon spyod gtsor gyur pa'i phrin
NK037(ji)012:130: las sgrub pa la ma mgon gzhan las kyang stobs
NK037(ji)012:132: sngon gyi mkhas grub rnams kyi gsung las /
NK037(ji)012:133: ye shes mgon po gzhan gyis las ma 'grub pa'am
NK037(ji)012:134: 'khyams rdugs byung na legs ldan bdud kyi rgyal por
NK037(ji)012:135: mdar sbran dgos gsungs pa'ang mgon po 'di nyid yin
NK037(ji)012:136: la / 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyi thugs las sprul pa'i nag po dug gi skyes bu dang /
NK037(ji)012:137: sangs rgyas kyi spyan sngar bden pa mthong ba'i nag po sde bo che zhes bya ba dang /
NK037(ji)012:138: dpal ldan 'bras spungs kyi mchod rten chen por bcom
NK037(ji)012:139: ldan 'das kyis gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor mtha' dag
NK037(ji)012:140: tu bcug pa'i nag po rdo rje 'jigs byed ces
NK037(ji)012:141: bya ba rnams kyang 'di nyid kyi mtshan dang sku'i
NK037(ji)012:142: rnam 'gyur kho na yin pas rgya gar du 'phags
NK037(ji)012:143: pa klu sgrub sogs kyis srung mar brten cing /
NK037(ji)012:144: bod du chos rgyal srong btsan sgam pos yer pa'i
NK037(ji)012:145: brag la 'di nyid bzhugs par gzigs te 'phrul snang
NK037(ji)012:147: gu ru rin po che pad+ma thod phreng rtsal bod
NK037(ji)012:148: la phebs pa'i skabs mgon po 'di'i sgrub skor mang
NK037(ji)012:149: po skal ldan rje 'bangs rnams la stsal cing phal
NK037(ji)012:150: cher gter kha rnams su ci rigs par sbas pa
NK037(ji)012:151: dang / bstan pa phyi dar gyi skabs jo bo rje dang /
NK037(ji)012:152: gnyos lugs sogs 'phags yul nas gsar du byon pa'ang ci rigs par byung ba las /
NK037(ji)012:154: slob dpon chen po d+ha na sam skri ta'i bka'
NK037(ji)012:155: srol gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches
NK037(ji)012:157: de nyid kyi skye ba du ma rgya zhang khrom rdo rje 'od 'bar gyis bton pa dang /
NK037(ji)012:158: gnubs chen po nas rim bar brgyud pa'i zam ma
NK037(ji)012:159: chad par byon pa'i bka' ma'i bka' srol yang chu
NK037(ji)012:161: zhang khrom dngos las dge ba'i bshes gnyen chen po rgya lcags ri bas gsan /
NK037(ji)012:162: de las mnyam med dwags po rin po ches gsan cing /
NK037(ji)012:163: gsar ma jo bo rje las brgyud pa'ang rgya lcags
NK037(ji)012:164: ri pa la bzhugs pas gsar rnying byin rlabs gcig
NK037(ji)012:165: tu 'dus pa ston chung dar ye sogs las brgyud
NK037(ji)012:166: pa dang / phyis gdams ngag la 'dra min bslad
NK037(ji)012:167: zhugs pa sogs byung na dag ther gyis sun dbyung
NK037(ji)012:168: ba'i slad du tshar gcig mtsho man+dala nag por gter
NK037(ji)012:169: pa dang / du sbas pa / phyis dwags po'i
NK037(ji)012:170: dngos slob skye sgom ye shes rdo rje'i sprul pa
NK037(ji)012:171: 'gro mgon dung mtsho ras pas spyan drangs pa bcas
NK037(ji)012:172: dwags po lugs la'ang bka' gter gnyis su byung ba'i
NK037(ji)012:173: rgyun srol gcig bsdus kyi rjes su gnang ba sgrub
NK037(ji)012:174: pa la sogs brjod nas man+dala 'bul du gzhug /
NK037(ji)012:175: thal mo me tog dang bcas te gsol ba 'debs pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK037(ji)012:176: rdo rje 'dzin pa dgongs su gsol //
NK037(ji)012:177: bdag ni 'gro la phan don du //
NK037(ji)012:178: gtso chen khyed la gsol 'debs kyis //
NK037(ji)012:179: ma lus rjes gnang bka' drin stsol //
NK037(ji)012:181: lugs 'dir rgyun bshags bya bar ma gsungs kyang gsang sgrub sogs lugs gzhan la yod pa dang /
NK037(ji)012:183: slob dpon dang sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' bka'
NK037(ji)012:184: sdod srung mar bcas pa'i spyan sngar skyabs gsum sngon
NK037(ji)012:185: du 'gro ba can gyis sdig pa bshags shing dge
NK037(ji)012:186: ba la yi rang ba dang /
NK037(ji)012:187: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa sogs tshul bzhin bya ba'i 'dun pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK037(ji)012:188: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK037(ji)012:190: de la thog mar dmigs pa 'di ltar du gsal thob cig /
NK037(ji)012:191: slob dpon nyid dregs pa can thams cad zil gyis
NK037(ji)012:192: gnon pa'i khro bo'i che btsan gsang bdag phyag na
NK037(ji)012:193: rdo rje shin tu khros pa'i nyams can /
NK037(ji)012:194: phyag g.yas rdo rje 'phyar zhing g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa /
NK037(ji)012:195: khro bo'i chas rnams kyis brgyan pa zhabs gnyis pad
NK037(ji)012:196: nyi'i gdan la 'dor thabs su bgrad pa ye shes
NK037(ji)012:197: kyi me 'bar ba'i klong na 'gying zhing brjid pa'i
NK037(ji)012:198: skur gsal ba'i mdun du thod mkhar 'bar ba'i nang
NK037(ji)012:199: du sogs gong gi mngon rtogs ltar brjod pa las
NK037(ji)012:202: yang sprul gyi 'khor dang bcas pa mngon sum du bzhugs par mos la /
NK037(ji)012:203: khyad par gyi don zhu ba'i slad du gsol ba 'debs pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK037(ji)012:204: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK037(ji)012:205: dpal ldan mgon po 'khor bcas rnams //
NK037(ji)012:206: ma rungs pa rnams bsgral slad du //
NK037(ji)012:207: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK037(ji)012:209: de ltar gsol ba btab pas /
NK037(ji)012:210: bla ma'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros mgon po la phog pas thugs rgyud bskul /
NK037(ji)012:211: mdun bskyed mgon po'i dpral ba nas 'od zer dkar po zla ba shar ba lta bu byung /
NK037(ji)012:212: khyed rang gi dpral bar thim pas lus kyi nad gdon sdig sgrib dag /
NK037(ji)012:213: sku'i rjes su gnang ba thob par mos shig /
NK037(ji)012:214: 'di la dmigs bsal ma bshad kyang bar mtshams rnams
NK037(ji)012:215: su spos dud rol mo re byas na rjes gnang
NK037(ji)012:216: spyi'i phyag len yin pas legs so //
NK037(ji)012:217: yang bla ma'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros mgon po la phog pas thugs rgyud bskul /
NK037(ji)012:218: mdun bskyed mgon pa'i mgrin pa nas 'od zer dmar
NK037(ji)012:219: po nyi ma 'char kha'i zer thag lta bu byung
NK037(ji)012:220: / khyed rang gi mgrin par thim pas ngag gi nad gdon sdig sgrib dag /
NK037(ji)012:221: gsung gi rjes su gnang ba thob par mos shig /
NK037(ji)012:222: yang bla ma'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros mgon po la phog pa thugs rgyud bskul /
NK037(ji)012:223: mdun bskyed mgon po'i thugs ka nas 'od zer mthing kha gnam sngon gyi zhun ma lta bur byung /
NK037(ji)012:224: khyed rang gi snying khar thim pas yid kyi nad gdon sdig sgrib dag /
NK037(ji)012:225: thugs kyi rjes su gnang ba thob par mos shig /
NK037(ji)012:226: de nas gtor ma thogs la /
NK037(ji)012:227: gtor ma 'di nyid legs ldan ma h+aa k+aa la
NK037(ji)012:228: bdud mgon trak+shada nag po dngos su gsal ba la
NK037(ji)012:229: mos gus byas pas khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor
NK037(ji)012:230: byon / de'i dbu gtsug gi nam mkhar rtsa brgyud
NK037(ji)012:231: bla ma sangs rgyas byang sems rnams kyang bzhugs nas
NK037(ji)012:232: byin gyis rlob par mos shig /
NK037(ji)012:233: dpal rdo rje nag po chen po lha chen dpal
NK037(ji)012:234: 'bar srog bdud trak+shada phrin las sprul pa'i mgon po
NK037(ji)012:235: chen pos / bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag po /
NK037(ji)012:236: slob dpon d+ha na samskri ta /
NK037(ji)012:240: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK037(ji)012:242: dge bshes rgya ston lcags ri ba /
NK037(ji)012:244: skyes bu ye shes rdo rje /
NK037(ji)012:245: 'gro mgon dung mtsho ras pa la sogs pa rtsa
NK037(ji)012:246: ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal ldan bla ma
NK037(ji)012:247: dam pa rnams kyi bka' dang dam tshig gi rim
NK037(ji)012:249: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK037(ji)012:250: sems can gyi bde skyid spel /
NK037(ji)012:251: bye brag tu rdo rje'i slob ma'am rig pa 'dzin
NK037(ji)012:252: pa 'di nyid dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid
NK037(ji)012:253: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang ma thob kyi
NK037(ji)012:254: bar du 'gal rkyen bar chad thams cad las srungs
NK037(ji)012:255: shig / mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad sol cig /
NK037(ji)012:256: mthun rkyen legs tshogs thams cad sgrub par mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)012:257: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa spyi dang khyad par 'di
NK037(ji)012:258: nyid la gnod cing 'tshe bar byed pa'i dgra bgegs
NK037(ji)012:259: gdug pa can thams cad myur ba nyid du tshar
NK037(ji)012:260: gcod pa'i phrin las mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)012:261: mdor na rdo rje'i slob ma'am /
NK037(ji)012:262: rig 'dzin pa 'di'i chos ldan bsam pa yid bzhin du 'grub pa dang /
NK037(ji)012:263: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i dngos grub
NK037(ji)012:264: ma lus pa yid bzhin du stsol bar mdzad du
NK037(ji)012:265: gsol / ces dang rol mo bsgrag /
NK037(ji)012:267: de ltar phrin las gsol bas mgon po'i sku las
NK037(ji)012:268: sku gnyis pa chad de khyed rang gi spyi bo
NK037(ji)012:269: nas mar thim pas mgon po'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK037(ji)012:270: ngo bor gyur par bsams la nga rgyal brtan por
NK037(ji)012:271: skyed cig / rjes 'brel bzlas pa'i lung sbyin pa la dmigs pa 'di ltar du mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)012:272: slob dpo na la mos gus dung ba zhig bskyed pas de'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK037(ji)012:274: de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng ram
NK037(ji)012:275: la sngags kyi phreng bas bskor ba las sngags phreng
NK037(ji)012:276: gnyis pa chad de zhal nas thon /
NK037(ji)012:277: khyed rang mgon por gsal ba'i zhal du zhugs /
NK037(ji)012:278: thugs kar nyi steng ram yig gi mthar 'khod par
NK037(ji)012:279: mos la sngags kyi rjes zlos lan gsum mdzad par
NK037(ji)012:282: gnyis bas dbyer med du byas /
NK037(ji)012:283: gsum pas brtan par gyur pa'i mos pa dang bcas
NK037(ji)012:284: slob dpon la me tog 'bul bzhin pas 'di'i rjes
NK037(ji)012:285: zlos / bcom ldan bdag la stsal lags kyis //
NK037(ji)012:286: bdag la 'go bar mdzad du gsol //
NK037(ji)012:288: me tog 'di nyid sngags kyi phreng bar byas te slar yang spyi bor bcings par mos shig /
NK037(ji)012:289: gsar ma phal cher gyis me tog la sngags lan gsum 'debs /
NK037(ji)012:290: kar lugs la mi mdzad kyang jo lugs la dgos
NK037(ji)012:291: 'dra bas de ltar byas pa'i me tog mgor lan
NK037(ji)012:292: gsum bzhag cing dril bu gsil la /
NK037(ji)012:293: bcom ldan 'di la stsal lags kyis //
NK037(ji)012:295: sngags kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK037(ji)012:296: brtul zhugs brtan par mdzad du gsol //
NK037(ji)012:297: rig pa 'dzin pa 'di rnams kyi rgyud la dpal
NK037(ji)012:298: legs ldan lha chen dpal 'bar tra k+shad nag po'i
NK037(ji)012:299: gsung rig sngags kyi nus pa ma lus pa 'jug
NK037(ji)012:300: par gyur cig / ces bzlas lung spyi dang mthun par byin nas /
NK037(ji)012:301: des 'di'i chos skor rnams nyams su len pa la
NK037(ji)012:302: dbang ba yin pas dam tshig la gnas par gyis
NK037(ji)012:303: shig / ces gdams la shis pa brjod /
NK037(ji)012:304: slob ma'i rjes kyi bya ba dam tshig bsgrag bzung /
NK037(ji)012:305: gtang rag man+dala sogs spyi ltar mthar dbyung /
NK037(ji)012:306: mdun bskyed gtor mchod kha gsos la slar yang gtor ma 'bul /
NK037(ji)012:307: mchod bstod nongs bshags bzod gsol /
NK037(ji)012:309: bdag bskyed bsdu ldang sngar ma byas na 'dir bya /
NK037(ji)012:310: bsngo smon dang shis brjod gang 'os bya'o //
NK037(ji)012:311: bstan bsrung kun las ches zab ces //
NK037(ji)012:312: rgya ston lcags ris dka' bar basngagasa //
NK037(ji)012:313: spu gri chog shur rgya mtsho las //
NK037(ji)012:314: gtor chog rjes gnang snying por dril //
NK037(ji)012:315: 'di'i lugs kyi lcam dral dang lha gsum ma dang
NK037(ji)012:316: 'khor mang sogs byed kyang 'di nyid 'don pa spos
NK037(ji)012:317: pas chog go // shin tu zab pa trak+shada dwags po lugs kyi sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no ////
NK037(ji)012:319: mchog gyur rgyal ba'i phrin las pa //
NK037(ji)012:320: phrin las mgon po la btud nas //
NK037(ji)012:321: gang de'i sgrub thabs rmad byung ba //
NK037(ji)012:322: lcags khab can du grags pa bri //
NK037(ji)012:323: bka' srol gsum ldan trak+shada ma ning ma'i sgrub thabs rjes gnang dang bcas pa la gsum /
NK037(ji)012:324: dang po sbyor ba yo byad kyi gshom ni spyir
NK037(ji)012:325: bshad ma thag pa'i spu gri gcig shur dang 'dra
NK037(ji)012:326: ba las / gtor ma g.yon phyogs su gtso bo las dma' ba gcig /
NK037(ji)012:327: mthe kyu bcu gnyis kyis bskor ba bya /
NK037(ji)012:328: gnyis pa dngos gzhi sgrub thabs la'ang /
NK037(ji)012:329: bdag bskyed he ru ka'i sgom bzlas /
NK037(ji)012:330: mchod gtor byin rlabs gong du bstan pa bzhin byas la /
NK037(ji)012:331: mdun rten swa b+h+aa bas sbyang /
NK037(ji)012:332: stong pa'i ngang las thod mkhar 'bar ba'i nang du nag po gru gsum gyi gzhal yas khang /
NK037(ji)012:333: de'i nang du mi ro rta ro brtsegs pa'i gdan la pad nyi'i steng du /
NK037(ji)012:334: ram las dpal mgon po sku mdog dus mtha'i sprin ltar nag pa /
NK037(ji)012:335: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas rtse gsum gyi mgul du
NK037(ji)012:336: mi mgo dpyangs pa ru dar nag po dang bcas
NK037(ji)012:337: pa 'phyar zhing / g.yon dgra bgegs kyi glo snying
NK037(ji)012:338: langs pa bun ne ba zhal du gsol zhing bdud
NK037(ji)012:340: sku la dar nag gi 'jol ber gsum brtsegs su gsol zhing /
NK037(ji)012:341: rin po che'i gser gyi ske rags bcings pa /
NK037(ji)012:342: stag ral g.yas su bkra ba /
NK037(ji)012:344: lcags gzhu nag po gru mo la gyon pa /
NK037(ji)012:345: tsan+dana beng chen sked la gzer ba /
NK037(ji)012:346: zhabs la lhwam yu ring gsol zhing /
NK037(ji)012:347: lcags kyi ral pa mun ltar gtibs pa /
NK037(ji)012:348: mche gtsigs spyan gsum sma ra 'bar zhing /
NK037(ji)012:349: thod skam gyi dbu rgyan dang /
NK037(ji)012:350: thod rlon gyi do shal can /
NK037(ji)012:351: rta nag chibs shing rdzu 'phrul dang drag shul che ba /
NK037(ji)012:352: me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)012:353: de'i g.yon du b+h+yo las yum rdo rje re ma t+ai dre'u nag po rkang gsum la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)012:354: d+r+wa ba mig dgu rgyab tu khur ba /
NK037(ji)012:355: phyag g.yas bdud kyi khram bam dang /
NK037(ji)012:356: g.yon nad kyi rkyal pa 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)012:357: spyan gsum mche gtsigs dbu skra gyen du bardzesa pa
NK037(ji)012:358: la zla tshes dang lte ba nas nyi ma 'char
NK037(ji)012:359: ba / dar nag gi lhab lhub dang zhing lpags kyi stod g.yogs re lde'i sham bu can /
NK037(ji)012:363: thal chen tshom bu sogs dur khrod kyi chas rnams rdzogs pa /
NK037(ji)012:364: snyan g.yas seng ge dang g.yon par sbrul dang dril bus brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)012:366: phyi sha la tshon gru dang byang dmar khres po btags pa /
NK037(ji)012:367: rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i dbus na rol pa /
NK037(ji)012:368: mtha' skor du lus dang grib ma'i tshul gyi sprul
NK037(ji)012:369: pa'i las mkhan mon pa pho drug mo drug bdud
NK037(ji)012:370: dmag bye ba dung phyur gyi tshogs dang bcas pa
NK037(ji)012:373: lce spyang dom dred rol du khrid pa'o //
NK037(ji)012:374: rang gi snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros //
NK037(ji)012:375: dur khrod chen po u tsa la nas /
NK037(ji)012:376: nag po chen po 'khor bcas spyan drangs par gyur /
NK037(ji)012:378: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK037(ji)012:379: dpal ldan mgon po spyan 'dren na //
NK037(ji)012:380: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)012:381: mchod pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)012:382: ma h+aa k+aa la tra k+shad sa pa ri b+aa
NK037(ji)012:383: ra badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh gnyis su
NK037(ji)012:384: med par thim / rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yi //
NK037(ji)012:385: lha rdzas bzang po'i nyer spyod 'di //
NK037(ji)012:387: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK037(ji)012:388: ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada sa pa ri b+aa ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK037(ji)012:391: nang mchod ces bsgyur ba dang /
NK037(ji)012:393: pany+tsa k+aa ma gu na ma h+aa a mri ta p+au dza hoh zhes phyi nang gis mchod /
NK037(ji)012:396: i dam ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:400: go ro tsa na la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:401: pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:405: srog bdud ma h+aa k+aa la ni //
NK037(ji)012:406: rngam pa'i zhal la gtum pa'i sku //
NK037(ji)012:407: gsod dang gcod pa'i las la dgyes //
NK037(ji)012:408: khyod la 'dud do bsam pa sgrubs //
NK037(ji)012:409: ming po rdo rje'i las byed ma //
NK037(ji)012:410: dam la gnas shing bstan pa srungs //
NK037(ji)012:411: khams gsum khrag 'thung re ma t+ai //
NK037(ji)012:413: shel g.yu dngul dang dung gi mig /
NK037(ji)012:414: mchongs dang zangs kyi mig can ma //
NK037(ji)012:415: sngags kyi rang sgra di ri ri //
NK037(ji)012:416: bcol ba'i las rnams rtags phyung zhig /
NK037(ji)012:417: srog bdud nag po'i dus la bab //
NK037(ji)012:418: legs ldan nag po'i dus la bab //
NK037(ji)012:419: ma ning nag po'i dus la bab //
NK037(ji)012:420: lha chen dpal 'bar dus la bab //
NK037(ji)012:422: de nas gtor chog tsam yin na rjes chog byas pas chog /
NK037(ji)012:424: bdag bskyed kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK037(ji)012:425: mdun bskyed kyi thugs kar phog pas dam bca' dran te thugs rgyud bskul bar bsam la /
NK037(ji)012:426: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada ga na gu h+ya ram sid+d+hi h'u phata /
NK037(ji)012:428: drag sngags tri yam ru tra la sogs pa ste skabs 'dir bzla mi dgos /
NK037(ji)012:429: rjes gnang gi don du dkar phyogs skyong ba rnams la dkar gtor zhig 'bul /
NK037(ji)012:430: de'i 'dod tshig rang lugs gang byas kyang khyad med do //
NK037(ji)012:431: gsum pa rjes gnang sbyin pa ni /
NK037(ji)012:436: sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma ka ras grub thob tsa hu pa la gnang /
NK037(ji)012:437: des slob dpon sh+aan+tim gar+b+ha sogs nas rim par brgyud pa bka' ma'i lugs gzhir bzhag pa'i steng /
NK037(ji)012:438: nag po sh+aan+tim b+ha dra'am rgya gar nag chen gyi
NK037(ji)012:439: lugs drag sngags kyi ngo bo shin tu rno zhing
NK037(ji)012:440: stobs che bas mgul khug lcags rgya can du grags
NK037(ji)012:441: pa dang / dam pa nag chung du grags pa
NK037(ji)012:442: pha dam pa sangs rgyas kyi zhu lo ts+aa ba
NK037(ji)012:443: la gnang bas zhu yi mgon por grags pa de
NK037(ji)012:444: dag gi byin rlabs kyi rgyun yang gcig 'dres su
NK037(ji)012:446: de lta bu'i rjes su gnang ba sgrub pa la sogs kyis sne bsgyur la man+dala 'bul du gzhug /
NK037(ji)012:447: de nas gong smos spu gri gcig shur gyi rjes
NK037(ji)012:448: gnang nyid cung zad kha bsgyur ba ma gtogs khyad
NK037(ji)012:449: par med pas bskyar nas bya ba yin pas /
NK037(ji)012:450: gsol 'debs nas bzung ste de ltar brjod pa las /
NK037(ji)012:451: mdun bskyed gsal 'debs 'di'i sgrub thabs ltar bya /
NK037(ji)012:453: sku gsung thugs kyi rjes gnang la 'od zer mi spro bar sku spro ba yin pas /
NK037(ji)012:455: de ltar gsol ba btab pas /
NK037(ji)012:456: bla ma'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros mgon po la phog pas thugs rgyud bskul /
NK037(ji)012:457: mdun bskyed mgon po'i dpral ba nas rang 'dra'i sku
NK037(ji)012:458: dkar po gzi brjid dang ldan pa dpag tu med
NK037(ji)012:459: pa byung / khyed rang gi dpral bar thim pas sogs gong bzhin la /
NK037(ji)012:460: mgrin pa nas sku dmar po /
NK037(ji)012:461: thugs ka nas sku sngon po spro ba ni khyad par yin la /
NK037(ji)012:463: trak+shada nag po lcam dral 'khor dang bcas pa dngos su gsal ba zhes dang /
NK037(ji)012:465: phrin las sprul pa'i mgon po chen po /
NK037(ji)012:466: yum khams gsum dbang sgyur rdo rje re ma t+ai /
NK037(ji)012:467: las mkhan mon pa pho mo /
NK037(ji)012:468: bdud dmag bye ba dung phyur dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis /
NK037(ji)012:472: slob dpon sh+aan+tim gar+b+ha nas rim par byon pa'i rtsa
NK037(ji)012:473: ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i rig 'dzin bla ma
NK037(ji)012:474: dam pa rnams kyi bka' dang dam tshig gi rim
NK037(ji)012:476: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs sogs snga ma ltar tshang bar bya /
NK037(ji)012:480: trak+shada nag po 'khor dang bcas pa'i gsung rig sngags kyi nus pa sogs sbyar ba las gzhan 'dra /
NK037(ji)012:481: slob ma'i rjes kyi bya ba dang /
NK037(ji)012:482: slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams kyang gong du smos pa ltar byas pas 'grub bo //
NK037(ji)012:483: kun tu zab par rab grags pa //
NK037(ji)012:484: mngon spyod 'dod rnams dga' ba'i gnas //
NK037(ji)012:485: mgul khug lcags kyi rgya can gyi //
NK037(ji)012:486: 'jug sgo'i thabs kyi snying po yin //
NK037(ji)012:487: dpal mgon po trak+shada ma ning mar grags pa'i sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no ////
NK037(ji)012:489: nag po chen po'i sku nyid las //
NK037(ji)012:490: bdud 'dul dregs pa'i lhar sprul pa //
NK037(ji)012:491: ma rungs kun 'joms la btud nas //
NK037(ji)012:492: gang de'i sgrub thabs bri bar bya //
NK037(ji)012:493: drag po'i las la cher basngagasa pa las mkhan 'brong
NK037(ji)012:494: zhal can gyi sgrub thabs gtor dbang dang bcas pa
NK037(ji)012:495: snying po tsam smos pa la gsum /
NK037(ji)012:496: dang po sbyor ba gshom ni spu gri gcig shur
NK037(ji)012:497: ltar byas pa'i man+dala dang gtor ma'i mdun ngos su
NK037(ji)012:498: / chos 'byung mthing nag gsum brtsegs zur dgu pa
NK037(ji)012:499: mi ro dang bcas pa bris pa'i steng du dmar
NK037(ji)012:500: gtor zur gsum rno dbal can sha khrag dang /
NK037(ji)012:501: yod na sku tsaka gis brgyan pa lhag por bzhag /
NK037(ji)012:502: thun gtor yang zur du bsham /
NK037(ji)012:503: gnyis pa dngos gzhi sgrub thabs ni /
NK037(ji)012:505: mchod pa byin rlabs rnams sngar dang 'dra /
NK037(ji)012:506: mdun bskyed ma ning ma ltar /
NK037(ji)012:508: me phung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)012:509: bar gyis mgon po gtso bo nyid gong non tshul du bskyed nas /
NK037(ji)012:510: de'i mdun du chos 'byung gru gsum mi ro can sum brtsegs zur dgu pa'i dbus su /
NK037(ji)012:511: skad cig gis las mkhan 'brong zhal nag po zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas be con 'bar ba dang /
NK037(ji)012:512: g.yon gri gug khrag 'dzag pa 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)012:513: stag ral dang gzig shub can cha lugs mgon po nyid dang 'dra ba las /
NK037(ji)012:514: dre'u nag po rting dkar la zhon pa /
NK037(ji)012:515: skad cig gis gsal bar gyur /
NK037(ji)012:517: dur khrod chen po u tsa la nas nag po
NK037(ji)012:518: chen po bka' sdod las kyi mgon po dang bcas
NK037(ji)012:521: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK037(ji)012:522: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs nag po che //
NK037(ji)012:523: rdo rje 'chang gi spyan snga ru //
NK037(ji)012:524: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas ltar //
NK037(ji)012:525: byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas 'di ru //
NK037(ji)012:526: drag po'i las la spyan 'dren gshegs //
NK037(ji)012:527: ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada sa pa ri b+aa ra
NK037(ji)012:528: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes gtso 'khor
NK037(ji)012:529: gnyis ka la spyan drangs la so sor bstim /
NK037(ji)012:531: ma h+aa sa ma ya ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK037(ji)012:532: ces dam rgya bstan la dam tshig dran du gzhug /
NK037(ji)012:533: rdo rje'i rtse mos nang mchod gtor zhing /
NK037(ji)012:534: mgon po dang rang gi lce thog tu myong bar bsam la /
NK037(ji)012:535: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK037(ji)012:536: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK037(ji)012:537: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK037(ji)012:539: badz+ra sa ma ya u da ka tha tha tha +aah h'u /
NK037(ji)012:541: lag tu rdo rje gtad par mos te /
NK037(ji)012:542: rdo rje 'di ni rdo rje che //
NK037(ji)012:543: sangs rgyas kun gyi byin gyis brlabs //
NK037(ji)012:545: nag po khyod ni nyams par 'gyur //
NK037(ji)012:546: badz+ra ma h+aa sa ma ya ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK037(ji)012:548: bka' bsgo'i tshul du thugs rgyud bskul la /
NK037(ji)012:549: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada tri yam b+h+yohn+ri tshal
NK037(ji)012:550: pa tri yam dzahdzah ru ru ru ru tsa pa
NK037(ji)012:551: la +aa shug me b+h+yoh zhes bzla /
NK037(ji)012:552: mgon po la sngar ltar sngags mchod tsam dang /
NK037(ji)012:553: bstod pa sh+lo ka gcig bya /
NK037(ji)012:554: las mgon la gtor ma 'bul na /
NK037(ji)012:559: i dam ba lim ta kha kha kha hi kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:563: go ro tsa na la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:564: pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:568: nag po chen po 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)012:569: bdag gis mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK037(ji)012:570: dgra bgegs ma lus bsgral ba yi //
NK037(ji)012:571: dmar chen khrag gi ar+g+ham dang //
NK037(ji)012:572: dbang po lnga yi me tog dang //
NK037(ji)012:573: rus pa rkang gling bsres pa'i spos //
NK037(ji)012:574: zhun chen gsal ba'i sgron me dang //
NK037(ji)012:575: rdo rje rang byung dri chab dang //
NK037(ji)012:576: sha chen sna lnga'i zhal zas dang //
NK037(ji)012:577: rkang gling thod rnga snyan pa'i sgra //
NK037(ji)012:578: dngos 'byor yid sprul mkha' bkang nas //
NK037(ji)012:580: gzhan yang mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK037(ji)012:581: 'bru bcud stong sbyar dza gad dang //
NK037(ji)012:582: rtsa brgyad stong sbyar bdud rtsi sman //
NK037(ji)012:583: dgra bgegs rnam gnyis bsgral ba yi //
NK037(ji)012:584: don snying sha rus gtor chen bshams //
NK037(ji)012:585: de bzhin tshe 'dzin khrag gi rgyun //
NK037(ji)012:586: b+han+d+ha lcang lo khrag gis bkang //
NK037(ji)012:587: bla na med pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK037(ji)012:589: mthun pa'i rdzas su bzhes par mdzod //
NK037(ji)012:590: de las gzhan yang mchod pa'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)012:591: zhing chen bla bre 'phan gdugs dang //
NK037(ji)012:592: rgyu rlon lda ldi snying phreng dpyangs //
NK037(ji)012:593: keng rus sna tshogs ri ltar spungs //
NK037(ji)012:594: sha khrag dri gsur rgyun mi 'chad //
NK037(ji)012:595: sna tshogs rgyan gyi mchod pa 'di //
NK037(ji)012:597: dam tshig dbang gis bzhes nas kyang //
NK037(ji)012:598: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod kyis //
NK037(ji)012:599: bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)012:601: las kyi mgon po ma h+aa k+aa la ni //
NK037(ji)012:602: sangs rgyas stong gi bstan pa srung ba po //
NK037(ji)012:603: bla ma dam pa'i sku dgra 'dul ba po //
NK037(ji)012:604: dus kyi gzugs can khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)012:605: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)012:607: gtor chog rkyang pa'i skabs 'di mtshams rjes chog bya /
NK037(ji)012:608: gsum pa gtor ma'i byin rlabs ni /
NK037(ji)012:609: gtor 'bul mchod bstod phrin bcol yan grub nas /
NK037(ji)012:612: de'ang dpal gsang ba'i bdag po dang //
NK037(ji)012:613: thugs rje chen po gnyis dur khrod chen po bsil
NK037(ji)012:614: ba'i tshal du bka' bgros te ye shes rtsa ba'i
NK037(ji)012:615: mgon po la dregs pa sde brgyad gdug pa can
NK037(ji)012:616: thams cad bka'i 'bangs su dbab par bka' bsgos pa
NK037(ji)012:617: ltar dregs byed ma lus pa dbang du bsdus pa'i
NK037(ji)012:618: tshe / dam 'og tu ma tshud pa'i gshin rje
NK037(ji)012:619: gnod sbyin pho mo nyer bzhi po rnams 'dul ba'i
NK037(ji)012:620: tshe / slad du / spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug
NK037(ji)012:621: gis byang shar u tsa la'i dur khrod kyi dug
NK037(ji)012:622: gi nags tshal chen po'i me tog rgyal po kha
NK037(ji)012:623: sbyor ba'i nang du thugs las sprul pa'i tshul bstan
NK037(ji)012:624: pas mon pa dung gi skyes bu'am /
NK037(ji)012:625: trak+shada bdud kyi rgyal po zhes bya ba gdug cing
NK037(ji)012:626: gtum pa'i ma rungs pa thams cad 'di nyid kyis
NK037(ji)012:627: ma thul ba gcig kyang med pas ye shes mgon
NK037(ji)012:628: po thams cad kyi phrin las kyi nus rtsal 'byin
NK037(ji)012:629: pa'i mgon po chen por gyur pa 'di nyid kyi
NK037(ji)012:630: yang sprul las mkhan chen po ma rungs kun 'joms
NK037(ji)012:631: trak+shada 'brong zhal can du grags pa 'di'i gdams ngag
NK037(ji)012:632: rnams kyang d+ha na sam skri ta las rim par
NK037(ji)012:633: brgyud de gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes kyis gter
NK037(ji)012:634: du sbas pa rgya zhang khrom gyis bton nas dge
NK037(ji)012:635: bshes lcags thang pa la brgyud pa /
NK037(ji)012:636: mnyam med dwags po rin po ches mtsho man+dala nag
NK037(ji)012:637: por yang gter du sbas pa nyid 'gro mgon dung
NK037(ji)012:638: mtsho ras pas bton te brgyud pa bar ma chad
NK037(ji)012:639: par byon pa'i gtor dbang bgyi ba la sogs brjod
NK037(ji)012:641: gsol ba 'debs pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK037(ji)012:642: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK037(ji)012:643: dpal ldan mgon po 'khor bcas rnams //
NK037(ji)012:644: ma rungs pa rnams bsgral slad du //
NK037(ji)012:645: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK037(ji)012:646: zhes lan gsum gsol ba btab /
NK037(ji)012:647: de nas dmigs 'dun 'di ltar du mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)012:648: gtor snod chos 'byung gru gsum mi ro can sogs gong gi mngon rtogs ltar brjod /
NK037(ji)012:649: dre'u nag rting dkar la zhon pa /
NK037(ji)012:650: dam ye gnyis su med par gsal ba de nyid khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor byon /
NK037(ji)012:651: de'i dbu gtsug tu lha chen dpal 'bar rtsa brgyud
NK037(ji)012:652: bla ma'i tshogs rnams kyang bzhugs nas byin gyis rlobs
NK037(ji)012:653: par mos shig / mdun gyi dmar gtor thogs la /
NK037(ji)012:654: sangs rgyas rnams ni thams cad kyis //
NK037(ji)012:655: sku gsung thugs kyis byin brlabs shing //
NK037(ji)012:656: dngos grub rnams gnyis 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK037(ji)012:657: gtor ma'i dbang bskur chen po sbyin //
NK037(ji)012:658: dpal nag po chen po bdud 'dul dregs pa'i dbang
NK037(ji)012:659: phyug ma rungs gdug pa kun 'joms las kyi mgon
NK037(ji)012:661: bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag po /
NK037(ji)012:662: slob dpon d+ha na sam skri ta sogs nas /
NK037(ji)012:663: yid bzhin du stsol ba mdzad du gsol //
NK037(ji)012:664: bar spu gri chig shur skabs ltar brjod la dril bu gsil /
NK037(ji)012:665: gtor ma mgor bzhag cing lag tu gtad /
NK037(ji)012:666: de ltar bka' bsgos pas mgon po'i sku las nas /
NK037(ji)012:667: nga rgyal brtan por skyed cig /
NK037(ji)012:668: bar shis pa brjod la me tog 'thor /
NK037(ji)012:669: slob ma'i rjes kyi rim pa rnams kyang spyi 'gre bya /
NK037(ji)012:670: mdun bskyed la slar yang gtor ma phul /
NK037(ji)012:671: mchod bstod dang bzod gsol bya /
NK037(ji)012:673: bsngo smon shis brjod kyi bar yang snga ma rnams dang 'dra'o //
NK037(ji)012:674: drag sngags kun las ches basngagasa pa //
NK037(ji)012:675: thal mo brdab chog rab dga' ba'i //
NK037(ji)012:676: sgrub thabs rjes gnang bcas pa la //
NK037(ji)012:677: yi ge snying po tsam gyis chog /
NK037(ji)012:678: trak+shada 'brong zhal can gyi sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no ////
NK037(ji)012:680: dus gsum gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK037(ji)012:681: kun gyi thugs las sprul pa yi //
NK037(ji)012:682: lha chen dpal 'bar la btud nas //
NK037(ji)012:683: gsang ba'i sgrub thabs 'bri bar bya //
NK037(ji)012:684: trak+shada gsang sgrub shwa na'i zhal can gyi bsnyen pa'i tshul ni /
NK037(ji)012:685: las sbyor dang sbrags ma yin pa'i phyir 'dir mi 'bri la /
NK037(ji)012:686: gtor chog dang rjes su 'brel ba'i bya ba tsam bshad pa la gsum /
NK037(ji)012:687: dang po sbyor ba yo byad kyi gshom ni /
NK037(ji)012:688: stegs bu'i steng man+dala la thod mkhar zur drug mtshon
NK037(ji)012:689: pa'i chos 'byung bsnol ma sngon po thod pa'i ri
NK037(ji)012:690: mo can gyi nang du gru gsum mthing nag gi
NK037(ji)012:691: lte bar thig le'am tshom bu dmar po che ba
NK037(ji)012:692: gcig / de mdun chung ba gcig /
NK037(ji)012:693: thod mkhar zur drug la re re bkod pa'i steng
NK037(ji)012:694: du khri'u'i khar dpal gtor gru gsum sku tsaka me
NK037(ji)012:695: ri dar gdugs dmar pos brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)012:696: mdun du thod pa'i bdud rtsi bzhag /
NK037(ji)012:698: drag mchod g.yas bskor du bsham /
NK037(ji)012:700: bdag bskyed he ru ka'i rigs kyi yi dam gang rung bsgom bzlas bya /
NK037(ji)012:701: mchod pa byin rlabs spu gri gcig shur skabs ltar la /
NK037(ji)012:702: nang mchod byin rlabs 'dir mi dgos /
NK037(ji)012:703: mdun bskyed swa b+h+aa bas stong par sbyang /
NK037(ji)012:704: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las gnam lcags kyi thod mkhar gru gsum bsnol ba /
NK037(ji)012:705: sgo med yangs shing rgya che ba /
NK037(ji)012:706: me 'bar zhing nad dang dug gi na bun 'thul ba /
NK037(ji)012:708: de'i nang du e las gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i steng du /
NK037(ji)012:711: n+ri las dgra bgegs kyi zhing chen bsnol ba /
NK037(ji)012:712: rang gi snying ga nas ram dmar nag 'phros te /
NK037(ji)012:714: ram las me dpung dmar nag ram gyis mtshan pa
NK037(ji)012:715: las 'bar ba'i me dpung gis 'jig rten gyi khams
NK037(ji)012:716: thams cad gang / dgra bgegs thams cad bsregs /
NK037(ji)012:717: slar yang ram las rtse gsum ram gyis mtshan pa las 'od 'phros /
NK037(ji)012:718: sems can thams cad bde ba la bkod /
NK037(ji)012:719: gnod byed thams cad tshar bcad tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK037(ji)012:720: rdo rje ma h+aa k+aa la srin po'i gzugs can
NK037(ji)012:721: sku mdog dmar nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis shwa na'i
NK037(ji)012:722: zhal rngam zhing gtsigs la spyan gsum bgrad pa /
NK037(ji)012:723: g.yas kha t+w+aam rtse gsum mi mgos mtshan pa phyar ba /
NK037(ji)012:724: g.yon dgra bo'i glo snying bzung nas zhal du gsol ba /
NK037(ji)012:725: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa la sbrul
NK037(ji)012:726: dkar khras thod bcings shing nyi zlas spyi gtsug brgyan
NK037(ji)012:727: pa / stag lpags kyi sham thabs dang /
NK037(ji)012:728: mi lpags kyi stod g.yogs can /
NK037(ji)012:730: zhabs g.yas bskum g.yon brkyang gi stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK037(ji)012:731: yang na dar nag gi 'jol ber gsum brtsegs gsol bar byas kyang rung ste /
NK037(ji)012:732: cha lugs lhag ma trak+shada spyi dang 'dra'o //
NK037(ji)012:733: de'i mdun du yum khyi mo gser mig ma /
NK037(ji)012:734: zur drug la g.yas skor gyis /
NK037(ji)012:741: bdun kar yang rdo rje dang zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK037(ji)012:743: g.yang gzhi stag lpags rus rgyan sogs kyis brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)012:744: srin po'i cha lugs can no //
NK037(ji)012:745: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis //
NK037(ji)012:746: dur khrod chen po brgyad nas ye shes pa sprin gtibs pa ltar spyan drangs par gyur /
NK037(ji)012:748: spyan ras gzigs mgon thugs kyi phrin las las //
NK037(ji)012:749: rnam 'phrul zhi bas 'dul bar mi spyod cing //
NK037(ji)012:750: drag po'i stobs kyis gdug pa tshar gcod pa //
NK037(ji)012:751: 'jigs pa'i gzugs can khyod ni 'dir byon cig /
NK037(ji)012:752: sngon tshe phyag na rdo rje'i spyan snga ru //
NK037(ji)012:753: trak+shada khyod kyis ji ltar khas blangs bzhin //
NK037(ji)012:754: drag po'i las la gnas 'dir spyan 'dren gyi //
NK037(ji)012:755: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)012:756: ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya man+dala ma ye /
NK037(ji)012:758: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya /
NK037(ji)012:760: a ba lo k+aa ya h'u h'u dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes dam tshig pa dang gnyis med du bstim /
NK037(ji)012:761: de nas gtor ma bsang sbyang /
NK037(ji)012:763: stong pa'i ngang las yam las rlung /
NK037(ji)012:764: ram las me'i steng du kam las mi mgo'i sgyed bu gsum /
NK037(ji)012:765: de'i steng du a las thod pa phyi dkar la nang dmar ba'i nang du /
NK037(ji)012:766: bi mu shu ma ra las bdud rtsi lnga /
NK037(ji)012:767: go ku da ha na las sha lnga bskyed /
NK037(ji)012:768: snying ga'i sa bon gyi 'od kyis mdun gyi nam mkha' la rdo rje h'u dang bcas par gyur /
NK037(ji)012:769: de las 'od zer 'og tu 'phros pas rlung g.yos /
NK037(ji)012:770: rlung gis me sbar sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga yi
NK037(ji)012:771: ge dang bcas pa zhu zhing khol bas lbu ba
NK037(ji)012:772: du gyur / de las 'od zer kha dog lnga 'phros pas /
NK037(ji)012:773: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi bkug nas de la thim pas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur /
NK037(ji)012:775: rdo rje thal mo kha gyen du phye la /
NK037(ji)012:776: mgon po yab yum 'khor bcas kyi ljags gtor ma
NK037(ji)012:777: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin can la reg cing gsol bas
NK037(ji)012:779: ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada ma h+aa k+aa la i
NK037(ji)012:780: dam ba lim grih+na grih+na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa
NK037(ji)012:781: hi / b+huny+dza ho rak+ta pi pa to /
NK037(ji)012:782: sa ma ye h'u kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)012:783: zhes lan gsum gyis gtor ma 'bul /
NK037(ji)012:784: mgon po'i thugs kar nyi steng ram dmar nag la bzlas pa'i sngags kyis g.yas su bskor ba las /
NK037(ji)012:785: bdag bskyed thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis bskul bas thugs
NK037(ji)012:786: dam dran phrin las rab 'byams thogs med du sgrub
NK037(ji)012:787: par mos la / ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada ma
NK037(ji)012:788: h+aa k+aa la drag po sid+d+hi tri yam du dzahdzah
NK037(ji)012:789: par mos la / 'bod pa'o // nag po he he dzahdza phata /
NK037(ji)012:792: tsit+ta rbad b+h+yo h'u h'u phata d+ha phata /
NK037(ji)012:793: bsad pa de gsum char gcig tu dril nas bazla'o //
NK037(ji)012:794: mchod pa spro na 'brong zhal can gyi skabs su bshad pa'i /
NK037(ji)012:796: nag po chen po sogs brjod /
NK037(ji)012:798: ma h+aa k+aa la trak+shada ma h+aa k+aa la sa pa ri b+aa ra badz+ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK037(ji)012:803: lha min dmag tshogs g.yul zlog cing //
NK037(ji)012:804: lha dmag dkar po'i dbugs 'byin pa //
NK037(ji)012:806: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK037(ji)012:807: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)012:809: gtor chog tsam la rjes kyi bya ba spyi ltar bya'o //
NK037(ji)012:810: gsum pa rjes gnang byed na /
NK037(ji)012:811: phrin bcol yan grub pa dang /
NK037(ji)012:816: de la chos skyong ye shes kyi mgon po chen
NK037(ji)012:817: po rnams ni dpal he ru ka dang rnam dbyer
NK037(ji)012:818: med pa'i byin rlabs kyi tshan kha che zhing mthu
NK037(ji)012:819: stobs nus pa'i gzi brjid 'gran zla dang bral yang
NK037(ji)012:820: mngon spyod drag po'i phrin las dngos kyis mdzad pa
NK037(ji)012:821: med pa'i phyir / sgrol ba'i thabs la mkhas pa
NK037(ji)012:822: drag shul can sprul pa las kyi mgon po dang
NK037(ji)012:823: med pa'i phyir / / de bas kyang yang sprul
NK037(ji)012:824: 'jig rten dregs pa'i tshul du bstan nas dgra bgegs
NK037(ji)012:825: thal bar brlag pa'i mngon spyod drag po'i las rnams
NK037(ji)012:826: thogs med du sgrub pas na brten sgrub mchod pa'i
NK037(ji)012:827: tshul yang so sor 'byung ba yin la /
NK037(ji)012:828: phrin las ye shes kyi mgon po nyid las srog
NK037(ji)012:829: bdud trak+shada nag po las mdzad du rnam par 'phrul
NK037(ji)012:830: pa'i tshul yang du mar bstan pa las /
NK037(ji)012:832: rtsod ldan shar du nye ba na lha dang lha
NK037(ji)012:833: min g.yul 'gyed pa'i skabs su lha min rnams kyi
NK037(ji)012:834: khrag sa la 'thor ba las dmag brgya stong du
NK037(ji)012:835: mar 'phal bas lha min la zad pa med cing
NK037(ji)012:837: ye shes mgon po 'di nyid dbang phyug ma h+aa
NK037(ji)012:838: de ba'i sras su skur sprul nas lha min rnams
NK037(ji)012:839: la mdung rtse gsum pas bsnun te bsad /
NK037(ji)012:840: khrag rnams sa la ma bo bar bar snang nyid
NK037(ji)012:841: nas gsol bas lha min 'grib cing lha rnams rgyal
NK037(ji)012:842: / gzhan yang lha min dang srin po'i grong khyer lan gsum bcom par grags /
NK037(ji)012:843: thub pa'i dbang pos bstan pa srung bar bka' bsgos /
NK037(ji)012:844: gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pas kyang gsungs /
NK037(ji)012:845: 'phags bod mkhas grub rnams kyis chos skyong ba'i srung
NK037(ji)012:846: ma chen por mnga' gsol ba bdud rgyal trak+shada nag
NK037(ji)012:847: po thod pa'i phreng ba can la sgrub thabs kyi
NK037(ji)012:848: bka' srol mang du byon pa las /
NK037(ji)012:849: skabs su babs pa gsang sgrub shwa na'i zhal can
NK037(ji)012:850: 'di ni sgrub pa'i slob dpon chen po d+ha na
NK037(ji)012:851: sam kri tas phung byed sh+aan+tim gar+b+ha la gnang /
NK037(ji)012:852: des rdzu 'phrul gyis gter du sbas pa spyi lha
NK037(ji)012:853: dga' rab kyis bton nas kha rag gi gnyos lo
NK037(ji)012:855: de la mgon po 'di'i bka' babs shing dngos su grub /
NK037(ji)012:856: rgya gar nas ba lim +aa tsar+yasa gnang ba'i gdams skor dang bka' gter gnyis ldan du gyur /
NK037(ji)012:857: snyan grags dang phrin las shin tu che bas brgyud
NK037(ji)012:858: pa'i zam ma chad par byon pa'i rjes gnang bsgrub
NK037(ji)012:859: pa la sogs brjod la man+dala 'bul du gzhug thal
NK037(ji)012:860: mo me tog dang bcas te gsol ba 'debs pa
NK037(ji)012:861: 'di'i rjes zlos / rje btsun rdo rje 'dzin pa'i gtso //
NK037(ji)012:862: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum gyi //
NK037(ji)012:863: dri ma mtha' dag sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)012:864: ma smin smin byed dbang bskur stsol //
NK037(ji)012:866: bla ma dang yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK037(ji)012:867: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i spyan sngar skyabs gsol
NK037(ji)012:868: sngon du 'gro ba can gyi bsags sbyong dang byang
NK037(ji)012:869: chub tu sems bskyed pa gsal thob la 'di'i rjes
NK037(ji)012:870: zlos / dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK037(ji)012:872: de la thog mar sku yi rjes su gnang ba'i
NK037(ji)012:873: slad du sngar bsgrubs zin pa'i mdun rten gtor ma
NK037(ji)012:874: nyid slar yang khyed rang rnams kyi blo ngor gsal
NK037(ji)012:876: mdun du gnam lcags kyi thod mkhar sogs mngon rtogs ltar brjod pa las /
NK037(ji)012:877: de'i nang du gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i steng
NK037(ji)012:878: du pad+ma nyi ma dgra bgegs kyi zhing chen bsnol
NK037(ji)012:879: ba'i gdan la / rdo rje ma h+aa k+aa la sogs nas /
NK037(ji)012:880: srin po'i cha lugs can no //
NK037(ji)012:882: khyed rang rnams kyang mgon po dam tshig pa'i sku 'di bzhin du gsal thob cig /
NK037(ji)012:884: stong pa'i ngang las e las gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i sogs mngon rtogs ltar la /
NK037(ji)012:885: zhing chen bsnol ba'i gdan la /
NK037(ji)012:886: sems nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo bo ram las rtse gsum sogs nas /
NK037(ji)012:888: khyed rang rnams rdo rje ma h+aa k+aa la sogs nas /
NK037(ji)012:889: g.yon brkyang gi stabs kyis bzhugs par gsal thob cig /
NK037(ji)012:890: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i h'u las 'phros pa'i 'od
NK037(ji)012:891: zer gyis sogs gong ltar spyan 'dren sngags bcas brjod
NK037(ji)012:892: / dzahmh'u bam hoh de ltar spyan drangs pa'i ye
NK037(ji)012:893: shes pa rnams gtor ma'i lha dang khyed rang gnyis
NK037(ji)012:894: ka la thim par mos shig /
NK037(ji)012:895: gtor ma mgon po chen po rdo rje ma h+aa
NK037(ji)012:896: k+aa la dngos su gsal ba khyed rang rnams kyi
NK037(ji)012:897: spyi bor byon te byin gyis brlabs par mos mdzod
NK037(ji)012:899: sangs rgyas rnams ni thams cad kyi //
NK037(ji)012:900: sku gsung thugs kyis byin brlabs shing //
NK037(ji)012:901: dngos grub rnam gnyis 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK037(ji)012:902: gtor ma'i dbang bskur chen po sbyin //
NK037(ji)012:903: ma h+aa ba lim ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)012:904: gtor ma mgon por gsal ba 'od du zhu ste
NK037(ji)012:905: khyed rang la thim pas gnyis su med par gyur
NK037(ji)012:906: te / sku'i sprul pa dpag tu med pa sprul dgra bgegs rnams tshar bcad par sgoms shig /
NK037(ji)012:907: des ni bum pa'i dbang gi don grub pa lags
NK037(ji)012:908: pas rdo rje ma h+aa k+aa la'i sku sgom pa
NK037(ji)012:909: dang ma bral bar gyis shig /
NK037(ji)012:910: gnyis pa gsung gi rjes gnang gi slad du /
NK037(ji)012:911: ka p+aa la'i bdud rtsi la 'jig rten gyi khams kyi dug rnams bsdus te /
NK037(ji)012:912: khyed rang gi zhal gyi sgo nas zhugs /
NK037(ji)012:913: snying ga'i sngags phreng gi me 'od dang 'dres pa /
NK037(ji)012:914: bu ga dgu nas spros dgra bgegs rnams la char bzhin phabs par sgoms shig /
NK037(ji)012:916: des gsang ba'i dbang gi don grub pa lags pas
NK037(ji)012:917: bdud mgon trak+shada nag po'i srog sngags bzla ba la
NK037(ji)012:919: gsum pa thugs kyi rjes gnang gi slad du /
NK037(ji)012:920: khyed rang rnams dpal ma h+aa k+aa la shwa na'i zhal can la yum gser mig mas 'khyud pa /
NK037(ji)012:921: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas /
NK037(ji)012:922: pho nya dang 'od zer gyi tshogs dpag tu med pa spros /
NK037(ji)012:924: shes rab kyi mkha' nang du chos 'byung ba'i mthing nag gru gsum gyi nang du bzhag /
NK037(ji)012:926: lus sems rdul du brlag par sgoms shig /
NK037(ji)012:927: des shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi don grub
NK037(ji)012:928: pa lags pas legs ldan dpal 'bar chen po'i thugs
NK037(ji)012:929: dgongs bde stong zung 'jug gi ting nge 'dzin la
NK037(ji)012:931: bzhi pa yon tan gyi rjes gnang gi slad du /
NK037(ji)012:932: de ltar dgra bgegs sgrol byed /
NK037(ji)012:934: sgrol tshul gang yang mi dmigs pa 'khor gsum ka
NK037(ji)012:935: dag spros pa kun dang bral ba'i dbyings su mnyam
NK037(ji)012:938: des bzhi pa tshig dbang gi don grub pa lags
NK037(ji)012:939: pas gnas lugs gnyug ma ka dag gi ngo bo
NK037(ji)012:940: rtag tu bskyang bar mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)012:941: gong ma gsum po nyid drag po'i las kyis bka' gtad yin pas /
NK037(ji)012:942: phrin las kyi rjes gnang la sogs pal mi dgos gsung ngo //
NK037(ji)012:944: dbang gi rjes kyi rim pa ni snga ma rnams dang mtshungs /
NK037(ji)012:945: mdun bskyed gtor ma'i lha slar gsal btab /
NK037(ji)012:949: gshegs bstim rten dang bstun la /
NK037(ji)012:950: bsngo smon shis brjod bcas bya'o //
NK037(ji)012:951: d+ha na sam skri'i sgrub thabs bzhin //
NK037(ji)012:952: gsal byed kun tu dga' ba 'di //
NK037(ji)012:953: yig sna'i don bzhin bsgrub pa la //
NK037(ji)012:954: nyer mkho'i lag len snying po yin //
NK037(ji)012:955: trak+shada gsang sgrub shwa na'i zhal can gyi sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK037(ji)012:956: zhes pa'i le tshan bzhi po 'adi'ang 'phral dgos lag
NK037(ji)012:957: tu len pa la rtsa ba'i yig sna gzhan med
NK037(ji)012:958: phyin mkho che bar mi snang mod /
NK037(ji)012:959: snga 'gyur phyogs su phrin las mgon po trak+shada ces
NK037(ji)012:960: grags che ba tsam las dbang dang sgrub thabs khungs
NK037(ji)012:962: mgon po'i rkang tshang ba'i phyir du zab cing khungs
NK037(ji)012:963: btsun pa rnams rje btsun thams cad mkhyen pa t+aa
NK037(ji)012:964: ra n+aa tha'i gsung rab las khol du phyungs te
NK037(ji)012:966: pad+ma gar dbang blo gros mtha' yas kyis rdzong shod
